<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>ltdẖkạry</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- min̊ ḥaẘli māyỉdatika .. yā rabãnā ạl̊ḥabīb̊
 nadẖ̊kuru maẘtaka ại̹lay̱ .. ạản̊ tā̊̉tī ʿan̊ qarīb̊

[V2]
 2- fahadẖā ạl̊kẖub̊za nā̊̉kulu .. naṣ̊naʿu dẖik̊raka
 ʿalay̱ ạảʿ̊sẖābiⁿ murãẗiⁿ .. nadẖ̊kuru saḥ̊qaka

[V3]
 3- wahadẖihi ạl̊kā̊̉sa ạlãtī .. tubāriku lanā
 taḥ̊kī ʿan̊ damika ạlãdẖī .. sāla min̊ ạảj̊linā

[V4]
 4- ạảmāma dẖik̊ray̱ ʿamalik̊ .. mādẖā naḥ̊nu naqūl̊?
 ạảyũ kalạmiⁿ yaṣifu .. ḥubaⁿ̃ạ fāqa ạl̊ʿuqūl̊?

[V5]
 5- lidẖā faṭība ḥubĩnā .. nas̊kubu fī kẖusẖūʿ̊
 yafūḥu biạl̊ḥam̊di laka .. yā rabãnā yasūʿ̊</lyrics>
<title>mn ḥwl mạỷdtk</title>
</song>